The '''Smiling Knight''' is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. He is not expected to appear in the series, being long dead by the time it starts. The Smiling Knight was an [[outlaw]] and a member the [[Kingswood Brotherhood]]. He was killed by Ser [[Arthur Dayne]], a member of the [[Kingsguard]] of [[Aerys II Targaryen]].
